dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents Assembly Districts for Wisconsin in 2011. Also included is a CSV file deliniating Act 43 Census Block assignments, Act43_Block_Assignment.csv.[These are the Assembly Districts created by 2011 Wisconsin Act 43. https://docs.legis.wisconsin.gov/2011/proposals/sb148.]
